# Lawrence Athenaeum and Mining Institute Act 1877Local Act1877 No 19

Date of assent20 November 1877

## Contents

[Title][0]
    
*   [Preamble][1]

[1][2] [Short Title][2]

[2][3] [Land vested in Lawrence Athenaeum and Mining Institute][3]

